reviewText:
Nooooope.

Low price does not justify low quality. Game could be justified with a few changes;

- Multiple creatures per level.
- Different coin values/speeds/stats for those creatures.
- Dinosaurs that don't run at the approximate speed of the African Land Snail.
- Guns substantially less powerful.
- Removal of the bloody slow motion shooting thing (or limited to say 1 in 10 shots). This is not Max Payne ok. ;--;

Ok. ;--;

recommended:
 and it tells;
- The UI. Menus are not very user-friendly and in-game UI is a little confusing;
- The walking. Sometimes the last animal you have to kill is 1500 meters away and you just have to walk and walk and walk and walk to it (your character gets tiret pretty soon and the default sniper rifle is not effective until you're at max 250 meters from the target). This can get boring sometimes.

